evenue but operates at a loss, driven by ~$3 billion in Starship R&D spending in 2025.\n- **AI** is in an early, investment-heavy stage — generating over $3 billion in revenue but posting ~$6.4 billion in operating losses in 2025, with massive capital expenditures ($12.7 billion in 2025, $7.7 billion in Q1 2026 alone).",
